data.description: Fantastic West Oak Ridge home, perfectly located on a whole acre lot! Tons of upgrades at every turn in this gorgeous Basement Rancher home. Brand new 2023 Tin roof. New paint throughout. The kitchen renovation includes, new granite countertops, new cabinets, a walk-in pantry built with tons of storage, stainless steel appliances, and a new sliding glass door that leads to the back deck and pool area. Updated upstairs bathroom includes new beautiful subway tiles in the bathtub, new airy light fixtures and mirrors. Crown molding added to the living room upstairs.Complete renovation of the basement and stairwell. New drywall, paint, carpet, and doors. The basement has it all including a large entertaining area, home gym, a sitting area or playroom. The basement also offers an additional bedroom and full bathroom with a walk out that leads to the massive fenced in back yard. The large carport is freshly painted as well.Within walking distance to Turtle Park playground, dog park, and hiking trails.Don't forget about the award-winning schools!!!Don't miss out on this gem!!!Items that will NOT remain on the property include: Electric Fireplace, Washer & Dryer, and the Swing Set.
